{"tid":1785586,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【黃色音樂圈】何韻詩旗人新人出歌喇","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:06.000Z","uid":261671,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"710c5380c2df2a3507b53ca2b613d2e8a71e5ebd","tid":1785586,"uid":261671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"係今年新人，佢叫林聰呀，啱啱出咗首歌叫「夜行」，hocc都有份作詞同feature首歌<br />\n琴晚淨係聽首歌，啲歌詞已經好催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱先睇埋個mv要喊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要大大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n/夜裡醒著的人，會在夢中相見。/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/urNn6mRP4Zk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FurNn6mRP4Zk&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=235efe0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/urNn6mRP4Zk</a>"},{"pid":"e5ae90aa04611d671361f1e51500c7c6a144e7ca","tid":1785586,"uid":261671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"／ 夜裡醒著的人，會在夢𥚃相見。 / <br />\n<br />\n夜行 (feat. Hocc)<br />\n<br />\n曲：林聰@goomusic<br />\n詞：林聰@goomusic, hocc@goomusic    <br />\n編：林聰@goomusic<br />\n監：蔡德才@人山人海<br />\n<br />\n帶著眼淚與失落<br />\n夜裏漂泊<br />\n如無人鐵幕<br />\n<br />\n掛念某日某一幕<br />\n彷彿聽到<br />\n仍同行作樂<br />\n<br />\n遺留下笑臉<br />\n漆黑不見天<br />\n始終相信 榮光中可再見<br />\n<br />\n放下怯懦去守候<br />\n此刻緊扣<br />\n有你我的手<br />\n<br />\n確信到尾再堅守<br />\n天空海闊 <br />\n天高地厚<br />\n<br />\n重臨舊戰地<br />\n火光中記起<br />\n當天相約 榮光中不放棄<br />\n<br />\n誰軟弱裏停步<br />\n誰挫敗中苦惱<br />\n誰捍衛中禱告<br />\n學會互相擁抱<br />\n<br />\n同照亮這前路<br />\n隨燈火的宣告<br />\n從告別中起舞<br />\n望有日終可到<br />\n<br />\n/ 這城睡了，人卻醒著 /<br />\n<br />\nGoomusic唱作新人林聰，<br />\n推出第三首單曲《夜行》，<br />\n首次與何韻詩一同填詞、合唱，<br />\n道出這數個月來香港人複雜糾結的情緒。<br />\n<br />\n二人相信，<br />\n新的一年來臨，<br />\n會有一股新的力量出現。<br />\n<br />\n#香港 #standwithhongkong<br />\n-<br />\n林聰 FB: @nichung<br />\n林聰 IG: @nichung"},{"pid":"715e297c0695e0cc2a2d51c1d0a431c52c79068c","tid":1785586,"uid":261671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"林聰之前出嗰兩首歌都好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iXJIdL9UDGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiXJIdL9UDGc&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=a041315a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iXJIdL9UDGc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fDn9NijIDS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfDn9NijIDS4&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=d27e7e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fDn9NijIDS4</a>"},{"pid":"31eb7b0be92c4115ca47b1f2456b7c61689349c0","tid":1785586,"uid":176114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩先睇完首播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59664d4816f063557e414a146c9312ea9ae1dd5a","tid":1785586,"uid":176114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"榮光中可再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhocc幾時會再唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等咗好似十世咁"},{"pid":"8e96c9c33d52afc83382063fe2985a896122e8c2","tid":1785586,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class